### Variables
@hostname = localhost
@port = 5000
@host = http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}/api/tasks

### 1. GET ALL TASKS (Should return an empty array [] or existing tasks)
GET {{host}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. CREATE A NEW TASK
# @name createTask
POST {{host}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Build the Frontend",
    "description": "Create the React UI for this assessment",
    "completed": false
}

###

### 3. GET ALL TASKS AGAIN (Verify the new task exists)
GET {{host}}

###

### 4. UPDATE THE TASK (Toggle Completed)
# Replace the ID below with the _id from the "CREATE" response
@taskId = {{createTask.response.body._id}}

PUT {{host}}/{{taskId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "completed": true
}

###

### 5. DELETE THE TASK
DELETE {{host}}/{{taskId}}